==艺术==
冈布茨启发了许多艺术家进行创作。

*由Ulrike Vahl执导的屡获殊荣的短片Gömböc（2010）描绘了四个与日常挫折和障碍作斗争的特立独行的人，他们都具有百折不饶的精神<ref>{{Cite web |url=https://www.imdb.com/title/tt1999171/ |title=Gömböc movie by Ulrike Vahl |access-date=2021-03-27 |archive-date=2017-02-10 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20170210153034/http://www.imdb.com/title/tt1999171/ }}</ref>。

*由Márton Szirmai执导的短片“The Beauty of Thinking”（2012年）是GE Focus Forward电影节的决赛入围者。它讲述了发现冈布茨的故事<ref>{{Cite web |url=https://www.imdb.com/title/tt3096186/?ref_=nm_flmg_dr_8 |title=The beauty of Thinking by Márton Szirmai on IMDB |access-date=2021-03-27 |archive-date=2022-02-27 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20220227084307/https://www.imdb.com/title/tt3096186/?ref_=nm_flmg_dr_8 }}</ref><ref>{{Cite web |url=https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=XOwez5hPuiA |title=The beauty of Thinking by Márton Szirmai on Youtube |access-date=2021-03-27 |archive-date=2020-12-24 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201224045229/https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=XOwez5hPuiA }}</ref>。

*丹·理查兹（Dan Richards）在广受赞誉的小说Climbing Days（2016）的风景描述中体现了冈布茨独特的形状：“在Montserrat，所有的景观都是冈布茨形状的圆顶和柱子。” <ref>Richards, D.: Climbing Days. Faber & Faber, London, 2016.</ref>

*概念画家{{le|瑞安·甘德|Ryan Gander}}举办了一个围绕着自正主题展开的个展，呈现出七个逐渐被黑色火山沙覆盖的大型冈布茨形状<ref>{{Cite web |url=https://ocula.com/art-galleries/lisson-gallery/exhibitions/the-self-righting-of-all-things/ |title=Gander, R.: The self-righting of all things. Exhibition at Lisson Gallery, London |access-date=2021-03-27 |archive-date=2020-06-14 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200614205759/https://ocula.com/art-galleries/lisson-gallery/exhibitions/the-self-righting-of-all-things/ }}</ref>。

*作为Vivien Zhang绘画中经常出现的灵感，冈布茨也在世界各地的美术馆出现过<ref>{{Cite web |url=http://www.contemporaryartsociety.org/artist-members/vivien-zhang/ |title=Vivien Zhang at the Contemporary Art Society |access-date=2021-03-27 |archive-date=2020-11-24 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201124034717/https://www.contemporaryartsociety.org/artist-members/vivien-zhang/ }}</ref>。

*2020年秋天，[[海牙|海牙]]的{{link-nl|Korzo}}剧院和[[比亚里茨|比亚里茨]]的剧院市政厅演出了法国编舞家Antonin Comestaz<ref>[https://theaterencyclopedie.nl/wiki/Categorie:Choreografie_Antonin_Comestaz {{Wayback|url=https://theaterencyclopedie.nl/wiki/Categorie:Choreografie_Antonin_Comestaz |date=20210204004749 }} Antonin Comestaz</ref>的单人舞蹈作品《Gömböc》 <ref>{{Cite web |url=http://dansercanalhistorique.fr/?q=content%2Fgomboc-d-antonin-comestaz |title=存档副本 |access-date=2022-06-03 |archive-date=2021-02-03 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210203042743/http://dansercanalhistorique.fr/?q=content%2Fgomboc-d-antonin-comestaz }}</ref>。

==媒体==
*冈布茨的发明成为了公众和媒体的焦点，这重复了1974年另一位匈牙利人[[鲁比克·艾尔诺|鲁比克·艾尔诺]]发明[[魔方|魔方]]时的成功<ref>{{cite news|url=http://www.theage.com.au/news/technology/is-gomboc-the-shape-of-things-to-come/2007/02/13/1171128948286.html|title=Boffins develop a 'new shape' called Gomboc|publisher=Theage.com.au|location=Melbourne|date=13 February 2007|accessdate=2021-03-27|archive-date=2017-09-07|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20170907115423/http://www.theage.com.au/news/technology/is-gomboc-the-shape-of-things-to-come/2007/02/13/1171128948286.html}}</ref>。作为发现冈布茨的表彰，Domokos和Várkonyi被授予了{{le|匈牙利功绩勋章|Hungarian Order of Merit}}<ref name=camb>[https://web.archive.org/web/20110606203346/http://www.admin.cam.ac.uk/news/dp/2009042702 A gömböc for the Whipple]. News, University of Cambridge (27 April 2009)</ref>。[[纽约时报|纽约时报]]将其评为2007年最有趣的70个想法之一<ref>Thompson, Clive (9 December 2007) [http://www.gomboc.eu/site.php?inc=0&menuId=12&hirId=5 Self-Righting Object, The] {{Webarchive|url=https://web.archive.org/web/20090915180628/http://www.gomboc.eu/site.php?inc=0&menuId=12&hirId=5 |date=15 September 2009 }}. ''New York Times Magazine''.</ref><ref>Per-Lee, Myra (9 December 2007) [http://inventorspot.com/articles/ideas_2007_9204 Whose Bright Idea Was That? The New York Times Magazine Ideas of 2007] {{Wayback|url=http://inventorspot.com/articles/ideas_2007_9204 |date=20210311001901 }}. Inventorspot.com.</ref>。
*邮票新闻网站<ref>[http://www.stampnews.com/stamps/stamps_2010/stamp_1290423039_172491.html Better City – Better Life: Shanghai World Expo 2010] {{Webarchive|url=https://web.archive.org/web/20170816060854/http://www.stampnews.com/stamps/stamps_2010/stamp_1290423039_172491.html |date=16 August 2017 }}. Stampnews.com (22 November 2010). Retrieved on 20 October 2016.</ref>显示，匈牙利于2010年4月30日发布了一版从各个角度展示冈布茨的邮票。翻动邮票册时，冈布茨模型就仿佛动了起来。这套邮票是和[[中国2010年上海世界博览会|中国2010年上海世界博览会]]上展出的冈布茨模型一起发售的（3月1日至10月31日）。{{le|Linn's Stamp News}}杂志也进行了报道<ref>McCarty, Denise (28 June 2010) "World of New Issues: Expo stamps picture Hungary's gömböc, Iceland's ice cube". ''Linn's Stamp News'' p. 14</ref>。
*冈布茨模型2009年7月12日在[[英国广播公司|英国广播公司]]的{{le|QI}}系列剧集中和主持人[[斯蒂芬·弗莱|斯蒂芬·弗莱]]一起出现<ref>{{Cite web |url=https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=XCAg5_vHFmI |title=存档副本 |access-date=2021-03-27 |archive-date=2021-05-19 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210519044033/https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=XCAg5_vHFmI }}</ref>。2020年10月1日在美国智力竞赛节目[[危险边缘|危险边缘]]中和主持人{{le|Alex Trebek}}一起出现<ref>{{Cite web |url=https://fikklefame.com/final-jeopardy-10-1-20/2/ |title=存档副本 |access-date=2021-03-27 |archive-date=2020-10-11 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201011135021/https://fikklefame.com/final-jeopardy-10-1-20/2/ }}</ref>。
*在互联网剧集{{le|Video Game High School}}中，第一季插曲Any Game In The House中，角色Ki Swan创造了一个儿童游戏中的拟人化的冈布茨敌人。
*2018年9月，冈布茨一单面[[骰子|骰子]]的形式在角色扮演游戏网络漫画Darths and Droids<ref>{{Cite web |url=http://www.darthsanddroids.net/episodes/1707.html |title=Darths and Droids |access-date=2021-03-27 |archive-date=2021-05-08 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210508015444/https://www.darthsanddroids.net/episodes/1707.html }}</ref>中出现。

